# Murua el al. 2012 Open-Loop Stability and Closed-Loop Gust Alleviation on Flexible Aircraft Including Wake Modeling

# Last modified: 19/01/2025
# 1: main wing
# 2: horizontal stabilizer
# 3: vertical stabilizer
