# F1: aileron: roll control (positive if rolling left)
# F2: elevator: pitch control (positive if pitching down)
# F3: empennage: yaw control (positive if turning left)
# F4: aileron: "flap"/WRBM control (positive if increasing lift)

# geometry and flight specifics have been checked the 16/01/2024 at 18:00


